11 O.S. Supp. 2025, Section 20N), which relates to Class
D1 criminal offenses; modifying certain felony
12 offense; creating certain felony offense; amending 21
O.S. 2021, Section 1162, as amended by Section 402,
13 Chapter 486, O.S.L. 2025 (21 O.S. Supp. 2025, Section
1162), which relates to purchasing dead body;
14 establishing certain felony offenses; amending 59
O.S. 2021, Sections 396.2, 396.3a, 396.4, as amended
